                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d269">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Goodnow</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-08-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 1, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>MacDonald courier 21st reports continuous artillery attack the 16th; holding
                    American, German, Russian legations, and part wall; food, ammunition short.
                    Sixty killed; 120 wounded. Japanese courier 23 reports the same.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Goodnow.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
